data.description: This lovely 3 bedroom,  2.5 bath Townhome has an attached garage and partial bsmt in the River Valley Village sub.   Kitchen features lots of countertop space, marble flooring & bar seating. This open floor plan home comes with all appliances,  Front yard has Trex deck and a fenced common area.  Livingroom has 20' ceilings and a gas fireplace. Master bdrm has an ensuite bath. Assumable loan 3.25% $240K with $180K down for qualified buyers.  Easy to show!
